<% invoice = params[:stripe_invoice] %>
<% amount_due = invoice&.amount_due %>
<% currency = invoice&.currency %>
<% next_attempt = invoice&.next_payment_attempt && Time.at(invoice.next_payment_attempt) %>
<% amount_label = if amount_due && currency
    currency.to_s.downcase == "usd" ? "$#{format('%.2f', amount_due.to_i / 100.0)}" :
                                       "#{format('%.2f', amount_due.to_i / 100.0)} #{currency.to_s.upcase}"
  end %>
Hi,

We tried to charge your card<% if amount_label %> (<%= amount_label %>)<% end %> for your TheraSaurus subscription, and it didn't go through.

<% if next_attempt %>
Stripe will try again automatically on <%= l next_attempt.to_date, format: :long %>.
<% else %>
Stripe will try again automatically over the next few days.
<% end %>
Until then, your profile stays online so families can still find you.

To update your card now and avoid further interruption, visit your Membership settings and click "Manage subscription":
<%= membership_url %>

Thanks,
The TheraSaurus team
